<p><a name="Published_during_Hugo.27s_lifetime" id="Published_during_Hugo.27s_lifetime"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Victor_Hugo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Published during Hugo's lifetime">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Published during Hugo's lifetime</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Odes_et_po%C3%A9sies_diverses&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Odes et poésies diverses (page does not exist)">Odes et poésies diverses</a></i> (1822)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Odes_(Hugo)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Odes (Hugo) (page does not exist)">Odes (Hugo)</a></i> (1823)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Han_d%27Islande&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Han d'Islande (page does not exist)">Han d'Islande</a></i> (1823) (<i>Hans of Iceland</i>)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Nouvelles_Odes" title="Nouvelles Odes" class="mw-redirect">Nouvelles Odes</a></i> (1824)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Bug-Jargal" title="Bug-Jargal">Bug-Jargal</a></i> (1826)</li>
